data.text:
- What is the price of the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET?

The price of the metal detector device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET is $ 189.00 .

- Why is the price of the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET in my country different from the price of the factory Nokta Detectors in Türkiye?

The price of the device in your country may differ slightly due to your country’s calculation of customs duties, shipping costs and other tax payments that are added to the price of the device.

- What is the country of manufacture of the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET?

The device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET is manufactured and installed at the factory Nokta Detectors in Türkiye

- Is there a metal detector store that provides the device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET in my country?

The device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET is available in almost all countries and you can find all store addresses in the list of distributors.

- Is there a warranty for the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET?

Yes, the device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET is sold with a two-year warranty period. Some device accessories do not have the same warranty period.

- Can I order the purchase of a metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET directly from the factory Nokta Detectors?

You can buy a device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET from the nearest distributor in your country, if the device is not available in your country, you can contact the factory directly and the device will be sent to you via express shipping service within a few days at factory price.

- What is the maximum depth of penetration into the ground detected by the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET.

This device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET can reach great depths underground if the treasure is large in size.

- Is this metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET German made?

The metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET was manufactured in Türkiye at the Nokta Detectors factory.

- Is this metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET original or an imitation?

The original metal detector is called Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET and it is made in Türkiye in a factory Nokta Detectors, beware of counterfeit devices made in other countries.

- Does the device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET detect underground to a depth of 10 meters?

The metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET can detect at great depths if the volume of buried metal is important.

- Does the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET distinguish gold from other metals?

Yes, you can with your device (the device) distinguish the golden metal among the rest of the other metals.

- Does the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET distinguish silver from other metals?

Yes, you can with the device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET distinguish silver metal from the rest of other metals.

- Does the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET distinguish iron from other metals?

Yes, you can with your device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET distinguish metallic iron from other metals.

- Does the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET distinguish bronze from other metals?

Yes, you can with the device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET distinguish bronze metal from other metals.

- Does the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET distinguish precious metals from other metals?

Yes, you can with your device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET distinguish the metal of precious metals from other metals.

- Does the metal detector Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET detect buried precious treasures?

Yes, you can with your device Nokta Pulsedive 2-IN-1 SET find ancient buried treasures.
